OL,3,CAmbulance workers threaten strikes
OL,4,Cover 'lack of breaks'
OL,6,FSome staff at South Western Ambulance
OL,7,Fstaff are threatening strike action
OL,8,Fover a change in meal break policies.
OL,10,FMembers of the GMB union are being
OL,11,Fballoted on industrial action over the
OL,12,Fdispute. However the trust says the
OL,13,Fchanges came about following feedback
OL,14,Ffrom crews and have been agreed with
OL,15,Fother unions.
