OL,3,CAmbulance workers threaten strikes
OL,4,Cover 'lack of breaks'
OL,6,FThe GMB union claims ambulance crews
OL,7,Fare forced to take their break
OL,8,Fwherever the nearest, often
OL,9,Fovercrowded, depot is and have been
OL,10,Fadvised to carry their food in their
OL,11,Fcabs.
OL,13,FThe union has health and safety
OL,14,Fconcerns over the new policy,
OL,15,Fincluding the risk of food poisoning
OL,16,Fdue to a lack of chilled storage and
OL,17,Floose food and drink containers posing
OL,18,Fa risk when travelling at speed
OL,19,Fresponding to an emergency.
