OL,3,CAmbulance workers threaten strikes
OL,4,Cover 'lack of breaks'
OL,6,FDavid McMullen, GMB Regional
OL,7,FOrganiser, said: "Workers face late or
OL,8,Fnon-existent breaks; crews are not
OL,9,Fallowed to stop until they hand over
OL,10,Ftheir patients, often 7 hours or more
OL,11,Finto their shifts or sometimes even an
OL,12,Fentire working day.
OL,14,F"There is a real concern from GMB
OL,15,Fmembers that this will lead to
OL,16,Fphysical and mental exhaustion putting
OL,17,Fpatients at risk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
