OL,3,CAmbulance workers threaten strikes
OL,4,Cover 'lack of breaks'
OL,6,F"If trust management doesn't start
OL,7,Fengaging with us, I can only see this
OL,8,Fheading towards a strike which would
OL,9,Fsee ambulance workers on the picket
OL,10,Fline."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for South Western
OL,13,FAmbulance Service NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,Fsaid: "The rest breaks and end of
OL,15,Fshift arrangements policy was
OL,16,Fdeveloped in response to overwhelming
OL,17,Ffeedback from colleagues who told us
OL,18,Ffinishing their shift on time was
OL,19,Ftheir priority. It was approved and
OL,20,Fcame into effect following agreement
OL,21,Fwith Unison, our recognised union.
