OL,3,CAmbulance workers threaten strikes
OL,4,Cover 'lack of breaks'
OL,6,F"We continue to work on refining and
OL,7,Fimplementing the policy fully and are
OL,8,Fcommitted to responding fully to any
OL,9,Fcolleagues who raises a concern. All
OL,10,Frequests for supportive measures and
OL,11,Freasonable adjustments are considered
OL,12,Fon a case-by-case basis."
OL,14,FIn a statement Unison said: "At this
OL,15,Fearly stage of implementation, the
OL,16,Frest break and end of shift
OL,17,Farrangements policy is delivering what
OL,18,Fwas intended in the vast majority of
OL,19,Fareas across the South Western
OL,20,FAmbulance Service NHS Foundation
OL,21,FTrust, which is very encouraging.
